title: Tales of Destiny 2 (Japan) (PS2)
description:
This is the original Japanese version of the sequel to Tales of Destiny. This is in JAPANESE. It is NOT the North American version of Tales of Destiny II (Tales of Eternia). This is in ISO image format. This game is for the PlayStation 2.

PLEASE NOTE: YOU NEED TO HAVE A MODIFIED PLAYSTATION 2 IN ORDER TO PLAY THIS GAME ON THE CONSOLE, OR PCSX2 TO PLAY THIS GAME ON THE COMPUTER.
